name: Rise
description:
13" x 19"
High quality archival watercolor paper
Limited edition of 50 hand-numbered prints
Each purchase includes free download of Adam's Castle "Vices" album.

Adam's Castle commissioned four visual artists to create a unique take on their "Vices" album cover, shot by Portland-based photographer Ben Canales. 'Rise' is my submission.

To see all prints in the edition and learn more about each artist, please visit: 
http://www.castleband.com/vices

name: Snoop Dogg- Show Poster Collectors Edition
description:
6 color silk screen
100lb. Hemp paper
19" x 25"
Limited edition collector series on special-order hemp paper. 50 signed and numbered prints by Tricia Kleinot.

You have to see these in person. The hemp paper really makes this print special. Get one today!

***Due to the natural inconsistencies in the thickness of the hemp paper, as each piece is made by hand, there are a few prints with small creases and folds. As the designer, I personally feel that these do not take away from the print in any way, but add to the unique quality of the poster. They are practically unnoticeable from viewing distance on the wall.***
